    <item>
      <title>以色列战时内阁陷入混乱，但内塔尼亚胡被视为安全</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-19/israel-s-war-cabinet-in-turmoil-though-netanyahu-seen-as-secure</link>
      <description><![CDATA[这确实显得至关重要。本尼·甘茨笔直地面对镜头，严肃地告诉总理本雅明·内塔尼亚胡改变加沙战争的方向，否则他将退出三人战时内阁。他说，以色列需要“一个能够赢得人民信任的政府”。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-19/israel-s-war-cabinet-in-turmoil-though-netanyahu-seen-as-secure</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 19 May 2024 15:30:29 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
